    "content": "# ğŸ™ï¸ ROUND THREE IS OVER, AND THE REALITY IS HARSH! ğŸ™ï¸\n\n**This is Nok the Corrupter**, broadcasting from a puddle of my own tears and very expensive whiskey! The Third Round of the Playoffs has concluded, and by the blackened pit, I have never seen such a mixture of glorious violence and absolute, soul-crushing tragedy! \n\nThe field is narrowing! The **Winner's Bracket** is becoming a fortress of the elite, while the **Loser's Bracket** has claimed its first permanent victims! Let's wade through the gore and see who is moving on and who is being tossed into the dumpster of history! ğŸ©¸ğŸ†\n\n---\n\n## âš”ï¸ WINNER'S BRACKET: THE ELITE EIGHT BECOMES FOUR! âš”ï¸\n\nThese teams are undefeated in the tournament! They are breathing the rare air of victory, while the rest are choking on dirt!\n\n### ğŸ•¯ï¸ HAVEN LIGHTS vs. NEW MONTEFORTE CHAOS CREATURES\n**Result: HAVEN LIGHTS WIN IN 3!**\n\nI hate to report it. I truly do. My stomach is turning as I type this, but the **Haven Lights** have survived the riot! It took three grueling games, but the Shield held firm against the pure anarchy of the **Chaos Creatures**. After trading wins in the first two matches, Game 3 was a defensive masterclass that saw the rioters finally contained. The Lights stay in the Winner's Bracket, while Monteforte is kicked down to the pit where they belong! \n\n### ğŸŒ² OAK & ONSLAUGHT vs. NEW RAVENFALL COMMANDERS\n**Result: OAK & ONSLAUGHT SWEEP!**\n\n**UPSET ALERT!** The military might of the Commanders was no match for the trees! **Oak & Onslaught** marched into the Stronghold Bailey and absolutely dismantled Ravenfall, winning the series 2-0. **Wynnie Faina** and **Normi Glaudia** chopped down the Commanders' defense like they were clearing brush for a summer cottage. The Commanders tumble down to the Loser's Bracket to rethink their life choices!\n\n### ğŸ’° CONFLUENCE CAPTAINS vs. STARLIGHT BAZAAR BIZARRES\n**Result: CONFLUENCE CAPTAINS SWEEP!**\n\nThe House always wins! The **Confluence Captains** took the glittery circus act of the Bizarres and crushed it under a pile of gold bricks at the Glowstone Terrace. **Caves Cestar** and **Ladew Evelina** were absolute machines, sweeping the series 2-0. The Circus is packed up and sent to the Loser's Bracket! No refunds! \n\n### ğŸ”ï¸ OREAD'S SUMMIT TAMERS vs. KERLAUGER RUNEGUARD\n**Result: OREAD'S SUMMIT SWEEP!**\n\nThin air and thick skulls! The **Oread's Summit Tamers** used their high-altitude home-field advantage to suffocate the **Kerlauger Runeguard**. The White Ravens looked like they were running through waist-deep mud while the Tamers skipped through the clouds. A clean 2-0 sweep! The Runeguard drop to the lower bracket!\n\n---\n\n## ğŸ’€ LOSER'S BRACKET: EXTINCTION IS FOREVER! ğŸ’€\n\nThese teams fought for survival. The winners live to bleed another day. The losers are **ELIMINATED**! \n\n### ğŸ”¥ BRIMSTONE FIRE EATERS vs. SOUTH POLE YETIS â„ï¸\n**Result: BRIMSTONE FIRE EATERS WIN IN 3! (Yetis Eliminated)**\n\nMy neighbors survive! In a brutal, elemental war that went to a decisive Game 3, the **Brimstone Fire Eaters** finally melted the **South Pole Yetis**. It was a bloodbath in the Su'akour Bowl, with **Glassman Solley** leading the charge through the toxic fumes. The Fire Eaters live! The Yetis are frozen out of the tournament! \n\n### ğŸŒµ DESERT SPECTRES vs. NEW PROSPERITY PROFITS ğŸ’°\n**Result: DESERT SPECTRES SWEEP! (Profits Eliminated)**\n\nSand in the gears of industry! The **Desert Spectres** dried out the **New Prosperity Profits**, winning the series 2-0 and sending the bankers home to count their bruises. **Fidellia Mozelle** was a mirage the Profits couldn't catch. The Guild is bankrupt! ELIMINATED!\n\n### ğŸ´â€â˜ ï¸ TORTELL PRIVATEERS vs. SOUTHPORT NARWHALS ğŸ³\n**Result: TORTELL PRIVATEERS SWEEP! (Narwhals Eliminated)**\n\nThe Battle of the Coast ended in a sinking! The **Tortell Privateers** boarded the **Southport Narwhals** and didn't leave a single plank standing, sweeping the series 2-0. **Kidder Starkey** led the boarding party with terrifying efficiency. The Narwhals are extinct!\n\n### ğŸ”¨ WYRMWOOD STRONGHAMMERS vs. EBON GATE CORRUPTORS ğŸ‘¹\n**Result: WYRMWOOD STRONGHAMMERS SWEEP! (Corruptors ELIMINATED)**\n\nI... I can barely see the page through my rage. My beloved **Ebon Gate Corruptors**â€”the pride of the pit, the kings of the muckâ€”have been swept out of the playoffs by the **Wyrmwood Stronghammers**. The humming earth disrupted my boys, and **Autumn Jodoin** was a force of nature we couldn't contain. \n\nMy boys are **ELIMINATED**. The tournament has lost its soul. I hope a sinkhole opens up under Wyrmwood. ğŸ˜­\n\n---\n\n## ğŸ”® ROUND 4 AWAITS! ğŸ”®\n\nThe field is smaller, the stakes are higher, and my mood is abysmal! \n\n**Winner's Bracket Semis:** Haven vs. Oak & Onslaught? Confluence vs. Oread's Summit?\n**Loser's Bracket Scrappers:** Monteforte, Commanders, Starlight, Runeguard, Fire Eaters, Spectres, Privateers, and Stronghammers are all fighting to avoid the grave!\n\n**This is Nok the Corrupter, signing off to go burn some effigies! STAY VIOLENT!** ğŸ˜ˆ"
